timeline.bodyText:
I think we can encapsulate this logic into a method to make it a bit clearer what's going on, perhaps something like:
nonProperties = removeDuplicatedDynamicTemplates(nonProperties, innerTemplateNonProperties);

Then the same method can be used below (where these lines are almost identical except for the maps passed in).

